commit.message: Finish converting codebase to use ruamel.yaml

Switch from PyYAML to ruamel.yaml

PyYAML uses distutils for installation, which is problematic with newer
versions of pip which refuse to uninstall it (as they don't have a
proper list of the files that were installed, leading to partial
uninstallations.)

ruamel.yaml doesn't suffer from this problem.
